ze-large aligncenter" src="https://businesstech.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/Starlet-interior-1024x682.jpg" alt="" width="840" height="559" srcset="https://businesstech.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/Starlet-interior-1024x682.jpg 1024w, https://businesstech.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/Starlet-interior-300x200.jpg 300w, https://businesstech.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/Starlet-interior-768x511.jpg 768w, https://businesstech.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/Starlet-interior-1536x1022.jpg 1536w, https://businesstech.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/Starlet-interior-2048x1363.jpg 2048w, https://businesstech.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/Starlet-interior-1200x799.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 709px) 85vw, (max-width: 909px) 67vw, (max-width: 1362px) 62vw, 840px" /> <img class="wp-image-434987 size-large aligncenter" src="https://businesstech.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/Starlet-moving-1024x682.jpg" alt="" width="840" height="559" srcset="https://businesstech.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/Starlet-moving-1024x682.jpg 1024w, https://businesstech.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/Starlet-moving-300x200.jpg 300w, https://businesstech.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/Starlet-moving-768x511.jpg 768w, https://businesstech.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/Starlet-moving-1536x1022.jpg 1536w, https://businesstech.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/Starlet-moving-2048x1363.jpg 2048w, https://businesstech.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/Starlet-moving-1200x799.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 709px) 85vw, (max-width: 909px) 67vw, (max-width: 1362px) 62vw, 840px" /> All Starlet models come equipped with safety and security equipment which include active electronic aids such as ABS, EBD, Brake Assist (BA) and Vehicle Stability Control (VSC). Automatic transmission models also include Hill Assist Control (HAC). Xi and Xs models are fitted with Driver and Passenger (D+P) airbags, while the Xr variants also feature curtain and side airbags (C+S). Pricing Toyota said that all Starlet models are sold with a 3-services/45 000 km service plan – with 15,000 km service intervals. A 3-year/100 000 km warranty is also provided. Starlet 1.4 Xi MT – R204,900
Starlet 1.4 Xs MT – R215,200
Starlet 1.4 Xs AT – R235,700    
Starlet 1.4 Xr MT – R258,500    
